PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
PREFIX si: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/si-builder#>

SELECT ?zoneLabel ?propLabel ?endpointLabel ?endpointType
WHERE {
  # zones
  ?zone a s223:Zone ;
        rdfs:label ?zoneLabel .

  # properties attached to the zone
  ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop .
  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .
  # keep only nonâ€‘writable properties
  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?prop brick:writable true } .

  # optional endpoint information (ALC / MPC)
  OPTIONAL {
    ?prop brick:endpoint ?endpoint .
    ?endpoint rdfs:label ?endpointLabel .
    OPTIONAL { ?endpoint a ?endpointType . }
    # keep only endpoints whose label or type suggests ALC or MPC
    FILTER ( regex(str(?endpointLabel), "ALC", "i") ||
             regex(str(?endpointLabel), "MPC", "i") ||
             regex(str(?endpointType), "ALC", "i") ||
             regex(str(?endpointType), "MPC", "i") )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?zoneLabel ?propLabel
